Class SortedList<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • List<E>
      • SortedList<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the data stored in this list
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>

    public class SortedList<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>
extends List<E>
    Allows insertion and deletion of elements while maintaining ascending sorted order. Also allows for the retrieval of elements by index, and checking if an element is or is not in a list.
